proc evaluate(symbols: openArray[State]; value: int): int {....raises: [],
    tags: [], forbids: [].}
This calculator evaluates postfix expressions using a stack. The following rules are used: If the next symbol is an operand (a number), put it on top of the stack. If the next symbol is an operator, remove the top two numbers from the stack, perform the operation, and place the result on top of the stack. * Source   Edit
